In the Czech Republic, too, the market’s response to the outcome of the vote of the US House of Representatives, which it had refused to support a stabilization plan for the local financial sector.
The Case of Stocks in Asia
A dramatic case experienced on Tuesday the stocks on the stock exchanges in Asia, although the indices were able to offset some of the losses over the course of the day.
